{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2807f3c335","title":"同意在朝鲜战争结束前推识解放金门","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a34bcb6457","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"2807f3c335"}],"tags":[{"id":"625c516d2c","name":"朝鲜战争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"b56e941465","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会代理总参谋长最荣臻1951年5月10日报告的批语。"},{"id":"c32b9aca68","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"楚荣臻的报告说：“在朝鲜战争未结束前，夺取金门之战以推迟举行为宜。估计攻占金门须经过剧烈战斗，各项物资准备必须充分。而在朝鲜战争未结束前，两方同时供应，力量恐来不及。因此所需船只以暂不集中和补造为好，以免形成很大浪费。5月12日，中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会根据毛泽东的批示，致电中国人民解放军华东军区：朝鲜战争未获决定性的胜利前，暂不举行攻夺金门的战役。为此，除现有的500般机帆船仍应分地进行训练与保养外，所缺船只暂不建造。"}],"contents":[{"id":"adcb2c7dea","type":"title","text":"同意在朝鲜战争结束前推退解放金门","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335"},{"id":"b56e941465","type":"paragraph","text":"是：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335"},{"id":"c32b9aca68","type":"paragraph","text":"同意你的意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335"},{"id":"b6bc643574","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335"},{"id":"2159e1bfce","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335"}],"page":{"id":"b4201f1198","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"2807f3c335","start":286,"end":286}}}},"__N_SSG":true}